---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About Me - Jonnykcode">
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <div class="border-b-[8px] border-black dark:border-white pb-8 mb-16">
      <h1
        class="text-6xl md:text-9xl font-black uppercase tracking-tightest leading-none font-serif italic"
      >
        The<br />Engineer
      </h1>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16">
      <div class="prose prose-xl dark:prose-invert prose-ink max-w-none">
        <p class="text-2xl font-bold leading-relaxed">
          HI, I'M JONNY. I'M A SENIOR SOFTWARE ENGINEER PASSIONATE ABOUT
          BUILDING SCALABLE WEB APPLICATIONS AND EXPLORING NEW TECHNOLOGIES.
        </p>
        <p>
          I created this blog to document my journey, share my findings, and
          help others in the tech community. Here you'll find articles about
          software architecture, frontend development, backend systems, and
          everything in between.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="border-[4px] border-black dark:border-white p-8 bg-black text-white dark:bg-white dark:text-black"
      >
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-black uppercase mb-8 mono italic">
          / TECH_STACK
        </h2>
        <ul class="space-y-4 mono font-bold">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <span>[01]</span> JAVASCRIPT / TYPESCRIPT
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <span>[02]</span> REACT / NEXT.JS / ASTRO
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <span>[03]</span> NODE.JS / PYTHON / GO
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <span>[04]</span> CLOUDFLARE / AWS
          </li>
        </ul>
        <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t-2 border-white/20 dark:border-black/20">
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="text-xl font-black uppercase tracking-widest underline decoration-4 underline-offset-8 hover:bg-white hover:text-black dark:hover:bg-black dark:hover:text-white transition-all"
            >GET IN TOUCH &rarr;</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .tracking-tightest {
    letter-spacing: -0.05em;
  }
</style>
